README.html.keywords: Setters LinksPlatform's Platform.Setters Class Library. Namespace: Platform.Setters Forked from: LinksPlatform/Helpers/Setters NuGet package: Platform.Setters Documentation PDF file with code for e-readers. Dependent libraries Platform.Data Mystery files .travis.yml - Travis CI build configuration. docfx.json and toc.yml - DocFX build configuration. format-document.sh - script for formatting tex file for generating PDF from it. format-csharp-files.py - script for formatting .cs files as a part of tex file. generate-pdf.sh - script that generates PDF with code for e-readers. publish-docs.sh - script that publishes generated documentation and PDF with code for e-readers to gh-pages branch. push-nuget.bat - Windows script for publishing current version of NuGet package.
